<div class="contact-form">
  <p>Wen möchtest du kontaktieren?</p>
  <fieldset class="switch_wrapper" id="message_target">
    <div class="switch">
      <input type="radio" id="admin" name="message_target" value="admin">
      <label for="admin" tabindex="0" role="button">Admin</label>
      <input type="radio" id="team" name="message_target" value="team">
      <label for="team" tabindex="0" role="button"> {{theme.short_title}}-Team</label>
    </div>
  </fieldset>

  <form class="admin_form hidden" action="/helpdesk" method="post">
    {{> "help/forms/form_admin"}}
    <button type="submit">Absenden</button>
  </form>

  <div class="team_form hidden">
    <p>Danke für dein Feedback, es wird direkt an das Entwicklungsteam der {{theme_short_title}} gesendet. Bitte achte darauf, keine passwörter und andere sensible Daten mitzusenden.</p>
    <p>Welche Art von Feedback möchtest du uns senden?</p>
    <fieldset class="switch_wrapper" id="message_type">
      <div class="switch">
        <input type="radio" id="wish" name="message_type" value="wish" checked>
        <label for="wish" tabindex="0" role="button">Wunsch</label>
        <input type="radio" id="bug" name="message_type" value="bug">
        <label for="bug" tabindex="0" role="button">Problem</label>
      </div>
    </fieldset>

    <form class="wish_form" action="/helpdesk" method="post">
      {{> "help/forms/form_wish"}}
      <button type="submit">Absenden</button>
    </form>
    <form class="bug_form hidden" action="/helpdesk" method="post">
      {{> "help/forms/form_bug"}}
      <button type="submit">Absenden</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>